_:Na152af5dedd24934af92724ab26cb78c <http://schema.org/image> <https://www.gov.uk/assets/frontend/govuk_publishing_components/govuk-schema-placeholder-4x3-194fde4197f00e669f6f52c182df2ed707bfb2024c9ef39f7a2ed20da62b90eb.png> .
_:Nb47cb13017eb4c9d9da54ad2cb46fa88 <http://schema.org/itemListElement> _:N9c4ee2d994ca4cd58e73d861dd8fa4db .
_:Na152af5dedd24934af92724ab26cb78c <http://schema.org/articleBody> "<div class=\"govspeak\"><h2 id=\"nuclear-waste-services\">Nuclear Waste Services</h2>\n\n<p>Nuclear Waste Services (NWS) is a trading name of both LLW Repository Limited (LLWR) and Radioactive Waste Management Limited (RWM).</p>\n\n<p>NWS is a division of the Nuclear Decommissioning Authority (NDA) which includes RWM and LLWR. NWS is not a legal entity but provides strategic oversight over the operation and development of these businesses through a <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/nuclear-waste-services/about/our-governance\" class=\"govuk-link\">management board governance structure.</a></p>\n\n<p>Make a new request to LLWR or RWM by contacting us using the details below.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact contact\" id=\"contact_4112\">\n    <p class=\"govuk-body\">Freedom of Information</p>\n\n\n    <div>\n        <p class=\"govuk-body govuk-!-margin-bottom-4\">\n          Email <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"mailto:FOIrequest@nuclearwasteservices.uk\">FOIrequest@nuclearwasteservices.uk</a>\n        </p>\n\n\n    </div>\n\n    <p class=\"govuk-body\">Nuclear Waste Services Limited (NWS Ltd) is a subsidiary of the Nuclear Decommissioning Authority (NDA).</p>\n\n</div>\n\n<p>If the information you want is not routinely published, you can make a request for it under the <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/make-a-freedom-of-information-request\" class=\"govuk-link\">Freedom of Information Act.</a></p>\n\n<h2 id=\"llw-repository-ltd\">LLW Repository Ltd</h2>\n\n<h3 id=\"who-are-we-what-we-do\">Who are we what we do</h3>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/nuclear-waste-services/about/our-governance\" class=\"govuk-link\">LLW Repository Board</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/nuclear-waste-services/about/access-and-opening\" class=\"govuk-link\">Site Locations and Contacts</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"what-we-spend-and-how-we-spend-it\">What we spend and how we spend it</h3>\n\n<h4 id=\"costs\">Costs</h4>\n\n<p>LLW Repository Ltd is a wholly owned subsidiary of the NDA.</p>\n\n<p>NDA is a non-departmental public body sponsored by the Department for Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy, and publishes a <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/nuclear-decommissioning-authority-tax-strategy\" class=\"govuk-link\">tax strategy</a> for the NDA Group in accordance with schedule 19 of the Finance Act 2016.</p>\n\n<p>As a result, LLW Repository Ltd does not publish a tax strategy.</p>\n\n<p>Information on expenditure, including income statements and financial reports can be found at <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/get-information-about-a-company\" class=\"govuk-link\">Companies House</a>.</p>\n\n<p>Latest LLW Repository spend data including expenses paid to staff and travel card spend is available on request <a href=\"mailto:foirequest@nuclearwasteservices.uk\" class=\"govuk-link\">foirequest@nuclearwasteservices.uk</a>.</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/1000045/LLWR_Grade_Structure_April_2021.pdf\" class=\"govuk-link\">LLW Repository Ltd Grading Structure</a></p>\n\n<h4 id=\"procurement-and-tendering-procedures\">Procurement and Tendering Procedures</h4>\n\n<p>LLW Repository Ltd procurement information is available <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/nuclear-waste-services/about/procurement\" class=\"govuk-link\">here</a></p>\n\n<h3 id=\"what-are-our-priorities-and-how-were-doing\">What are our priorities and how we’re doing</h3>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/llwr-plan-2018-to-2023\" class=\"govuk-link\">The LLWR Plan</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/llwr-social-impact-plan-2020-2023\" class=\"govuk-link\">LLW Repository Ltd Social Impact plan</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/llwr-sme-action-plan-march-2019\" class=\"govuk-link\">LLW Repository Ltd Small Medium Enterprise action plan</a></p>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"our-policies-and-procedures\">Our policies and procedures</h3>\n<p>It is our intent to publish a range of additional policies and procedures in this section as we move forward, covering issues such as corporate governance, health and safety and financial management.</p>\n\n<h4 id=\"policy-and-procedures-for-the-provision-of-service-and-conduct-of-business\">Policy and procedures for the provision of service and conduct of business</h4>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <p><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/971628/LLWR_Ltd_-_Gender_Pay_Gap_Report_2020__Final_.pdf\" class=\"govuk-link\">LLWR Gender Pay Gap Report</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/nuclear-waste-services/about/personal-information-charter\" class=\"govuk-link\">Personal Information Charter</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/979260/Policy_051_Sustainability_Policy.pdf\" class=\"govuk-link\">Sustainability Policy</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/nuclear-waste-services/about/accessible-documents-policy\" class=\"govuk-link\">Accessible Documents Policy</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/1048992/Policy_004_EHSQ_Policy.pdf\" class=\"govuk-link\">EHS&amp;Q Policy</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/1049045/Policy_046_Business_Continuity_Policy.pdf\" class=\"govuk-link\">Business Continuity Policy</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/1049047/Policy_047_Risk_Management_Policy.pdf\" class=\"govuk-link\">Risk Management Policy</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/1049049/Policy_048_Security_in_the_Supply_Chain.pdf\" class=\"govuk-link\">Security in the Supply Chain Policy</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/1049042/Policy_043_Procurement_and_Supply_Chain_Policy.pdf\" class=\"govuk-link\">Procurement and Supply Chain Policy</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/1048986/Policy_001_Cyber_Security_and_Information_Assurance_Policy.pdf\" class=\"govuk-link\">Cyber Security and Information Assurance Policy</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/1049002/Policy_034_IS_T_Policy.pdf\" class=\"govuk-link\">IS&amp;T Policy</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/1048987/Policy_002_Knowledge_Management_Policy.pdf\" class=\"govuk-link\">Knowledge Management Policy</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/1048990/Policy_003_Asset_Management_Policy.doc.pdf\" class=\"govuk-link\">Asset Management Policy</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/1049000/Policy_025_Security_Policy.pdf\" class=\"govuk-link\">Security Policy</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/1049006/Policy_036_Information_Risk_Management_Policy.pdf\" class=\"govuk-link\">Information Risk Management Policy</a></p>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4 id=\"policy-and-procedures-for-the-recruitment-and-employment-of-employees\">Policy and procedures for the recruitment and employment of employees</h4>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/nuclear-waste-services-modern-slavery-and-human-trafficking-statements\" class=\"govuk-link\">Modern Slavery and Human Trafficking Policy</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/1049050/Policy_050_Mental_Health_and_Well_Being_Policy.pdf\" class=\"govuk-link\">Mental Health and Well Being Policy</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/1048993/Policy_006_Equality_Policy.pdf\" class=\"govuk-link\">Equality Policy</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/1049043/Policy_045_Travel_Safety_Policy.pdf\" class=\"govuk-link\">Travel Safety Policy</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/1048994/Policy_007_Respect_at_Work.pdf\" class=\"govuk-link\">Respect at Work Policy</a></p>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"nda-group-documents\">NDA Group Documents</h3>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/nuclear-decommissioning-authority-annual-report-and-accounts-2020-to-2021/nda-annual-report-and-accounts-2020-to-2021\" class=\"govuk-link\">NDA Annual Report and Accounts 2020-2021</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/971510/NDA_Business_Plan_2021-2024_170321.pdf\" class=\"govuk-link\">NDA Business Plan</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/969608/NDA_Strategy_Stakeholder_Response_Report_2021.pdf\" class=\"govuk-link\">NDA Strategy Stakeholder Report 2020-2021</a></p>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"list-and-registers\">List and registers</h3>\n<p>Register of directors’ interests will be provided shortly.</p>\n\n<p>LLW Repository Ltd uses CCTV for the purpose of crime prevention/detection, employee safety and the protection of property on and immediately around all of its sites.</p>\n\n<p>CCTV surveillance is controlled by: Nuclear Decommissioning Authority/LLW Repository Ltd.</p>\n\n<p>A register of gifts and hospitality provided to board members and senior personnel is available on request from <a href=\"mailto:foirequest@nuclearwasteservices.uk\" class=\"govuk-link\">foirequest@nuclearwasteservices.uk</a>.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"any-registers-of-interests-kept-by-the-company\">Any registers of interests kept by the company</h3>\n<p>LLW Repository Ltd has no interest in any other companies.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"radioactive-waste-management-ltd\">Radioactive Waste Management Ltd</h2>\n\n<h3 id=\"who-we-are-and-what-we-do\">Who we are and what we do</h3>\n\n<p>You can <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/radioactive-waste-management\" class=\"govuk-link\">find our contact information on our home page</a></p>\n\n<h4 id=\"roles-and-responsibilities\">Roles and responsibilities</h4>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>You can <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/radioactive-waste-management/about\" class=\"govuk-link\">find out about our roles and responsibilities</a>\n</li>\n  <li>Our <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/radioactive-waste-management/about/our-governance\" class=\"govuk-link\">Board and Executive Team</a>\n</li>\n  <li>Our <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/radioactive-waste-management-organisation-chart?cachebust=1442924871&amp;preview=545291\" class=\"govuk-link\">organisation chart</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"what-we-spend-and-how-we-spend-it-1\">What we spend and how we spend it</h3>\n\n<h4 id=\"costs-1\">Costs</h4>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <p>Information on our expenditure is held within our <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link\">\n  <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/61f2b58d8fa8f538879fb1d4/RWM_Annual_Review_2019_20_English.pdf_safe.pdf\">RWM Annual Report and Accounts 2019 to 2020</a>  (<span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\" class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__abbr\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">5.69 MB</span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">24 pages</span>)</span></p>\n  </li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/radioactive-waste-management-ltd-spend-and-expense-data-april-2014-to-current\" class=\"govuk-link\">Spend data – invoices paid to contractors and expenses paid to staff</a></li>\n  <li>Our pay scales and grading structure are held in <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link\">\n  <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/61f2b58cd3bf7f78e469cd12/03_RWM_Roles_and_Salary_Ranges_Apr_20.pdf_safe.pdf\">RWM roles and salary ranges April 2020</a>  (<span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\" class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__abbr\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">106 KB</span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">3 pages</span>)</span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4 id=\"procurement-and-tendering-procedures-1\">Procurement and tendering procedures</h4>\n\n<p>RWM follows the procedures that have been developed by NDA. All suppliers of goods and services to the RWM should familiarise themselves with our Terms and Conditions.</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/452407/General_Terms_and_Condition_of_Contract_for_Consultants_and_Contractors.pdf\" class=\"govuk-link\">General Terms and Condition of Contract for Suppliers or Contractors</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>General Terms and Conditions of Contract - Purchase of Goods and Services</p>\n  </li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/539743/IPPR01-TAC09_Information_security_responsibilities_for_contractors_handling_official_documents_outside_NDA_premises.pdf\" class=\"govuk-link\">Information security responsibilities for contractors handling official documents outside NDA premises</a></li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/539745/IPPR01-TAC11_-_Contractors_working_in_non-NDA_locations.pdf\" class=\"govuk-link\">Contractors working in non-NDA locations</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/539744/IPPR01-TAC10_Cyber_Essentials_in_the_NDA.pdf\" class=\"govuk-link\">Cyber Essentials in the NDA</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>Details of <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/radioactive-waste-management/about/procurement\" class=\"govuk-link\">our approach to procurement</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>Lists of contract opportunities and awards with details of value are available via <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.contractsfinder.service.gov.uk/Search\" class=\"govuk-link\">Contracts Finder</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"what-our-priorities-are-and-how-we-are-doing\">What our priorities are and how we are doing</h3>\n\n<h4 id=\"rwms-priorities\">RWM’s priorities</h4>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/835903/RWM_Corporate_Strategy_2019_a.pdf\" class=\"govuk-link\">Corporate Strategy 2019</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/hsse-and-quality-strategy-2020-2025\" class=\"govuk-link\">Health, Safety, Security, Safeguards, Environment and Quality Strategy</a></li>\n  <li><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/931865/Science_and_Technology_Plan_2020.pdf\" class=\"govuk-link\">Science and Technology Plan</a></li>\n  <li><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://rwm.nda.gov.uk/issues/\" class=\"govuk-link\">Geological Disposal Facility Issues Register</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4 id=\"how-rwm-is-doing\">How RWM is doing</h4>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link\">\n  <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/61f2b58c8fa8f5388cafda85/Annual_Report_and_Financial_Statements_2019_20.pdf_safe.pdf\">Annual Report and Financial Statements 2019 to 2020</a>  (<span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\" class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__abbr\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">440 KB</span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">36 pages</span>)</span></li>\n  <li>Our <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/disposability-assessment-process-report-on-customer-feedback\" class=\"govuk-link\">disposability assessment customer feedback</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"how-we-make-decisions\">How we make decisions</h3>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/radioactive-waste-management/about/our-governance\" class=\"govuk-link\">The minutes of the RWM Board</a></p>\n\n<h3 id=\"our-policies-and-procedures-1\">Our policies and procedures</h3>\n\n<h4 id=\"policies-and-procedures-for-the-provision-of-services-and-conduct-of-business\">Policies and procedures for the provision of services and conduct of business:</h4>\n\n<p>You can find the following below.</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link\">\n  <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/61f2b58de90e07689b388fd7/RWP104_-_Information_Governance_Policy.pdf\">RWM Information Governance Policy</a>  (<span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\" class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__abbr\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">716 KB</span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">5 pages</span>)</span></li>\n  <li><span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link\">\n  <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/61f2b58c8fa8f5388a7ccc86/05_RWP50_Health__Safety__Security__Environmental_and_Quality__HSSEQ__Policy_AccessibilityChecked.pdf_safe.pdf\">RWM Health, Safety, Security, Environmental and Quality (HSSEQ) Policy</a>  (<span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\" class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__abbr\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">6.15 MB</span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">4 pages</span>)</span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>RWM has adopted NDA’s policies in the following areas:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/nda-intellectual-property-policy\" class=\"govuk-link\">Intellectual Property Policy</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4 id=\"policies-and-procedures-for-the-recruitment-and-employment-of-staff\">Policies and procedures for the recruitment and employment of staff:</h4>\n\n<p>RWM has adopted NDA’s policies in these areas:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/nda-equal-opportunities-and-diversity-policy\" class=\"govuk-link\">Equal Opportunities, Harassment, Discrimination and Diversity Policy</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/nda-anti-fraud-bribery-and-corruption-policy\" class=\"govuk-link\">Anti-Fraud, Bribery and Corruption Policy</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>You can find the following policies below:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link\">\n  <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/61f2b58c8fa8f5388a7ccc86/05_RWP50_Health__Safety__Security__Environmental_and_Quality__HSSEQ__Policy_AccessibilityChecked.pdf_safe.pdf\">RWM Health, Safety, Security, Environmental and Quality (HSSEQ) Policy</a>  (<span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\" class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__abbr\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">6.15 MB</span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">4 pages</span>)</span></li>\n  <li><span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link\">\n  <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/61f2b58c8fa8f5388b582d24/06_RWPR131_Travel_and_Expenses_AccessibilityChecked.pdf_safe.pdf\">RWM Travel and Expenses Policy</a>  (<span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\" class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__abbr\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">776 KB</span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">11 pages</span>)</span></li>\n  <li><span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link\">\n  <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/61f2b58ce90e07689cd9a94f/07_HRP05_Whistle_Blowing_Policy_AccessibilityChecked.pdf_safe.pdf\">RWM Whistleblowing Policy</a>  (<span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\" class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__abbr\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">238 KB</span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">3 pages</span>)</span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"policies-and-procedures-for-customer-service\">Policies and procedures for customer service</h3>\n\n<p>You can find the following policies below:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link\">\n  <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/61f2b58c8fa8f5388e978114/08_RWPR57_Customer_Complaints_AccessibilityChecked.pdf_safe.pdf\">RWM Customer Complaints Policy</a>  (<span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\" class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__abbr\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">128 KB</span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">5 pages</span>)</span></li>\n  <li><span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link\">\n  <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/61f2b58d8fa8f5388cafda86/RWPR72__Processing_requests_for_information.pdf\">RWM Processing requests for information</a>  (<span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\" class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__abbr\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">798 KB</span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">14 pages</span>)</span></li>\n  <li><span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link\">\n  <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/61f2b58cd3bf7f78e7e15a24/10_RWPR74_Internal_Review_of_Information_Request_Complaints_AccessibilityChecked.pdf_safe.pdf\">RWM Internal Review of Information Request Complaints</a>  (<span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\" class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__abbr\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">145 KB</span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">10 pages</span>)</span></li>\n  <li><span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link\">\n  <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/61f2b58ce90e07689cd9a94f/07_HRP05_Whistle_Blowing_Policy_AccessibilityChecked.pdf_safe.pdf\">RWM Whistleblowing Policy</a>  (<span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\" class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__abbr\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">238 KB</span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">3 pages</span>)</span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4 id=\"policies-and-procedures-for-records-management-and-personal-data\">Policies and procedures for records management and personal data:</h4>\n\n<p>You can find the following policies below:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link\">\n  <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/61f2b58de90e07689b388fd7/RWP104_-_Information_Governance_Policy.pdf\">RWM Information Governance Policy</a>  (<span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\" class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__abbr\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">716 KB</span>, <span class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\">5 pages</span>)</span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"lists-and-registers\">Lists and registers</h3>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"mailto:gdfenquiries@nda.gov.uk\" class=\"govuk-link\">Register of gifts and hospitality - available on request</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"mailto:gdfenquiries@nda.gov.uk\" class=\"govuk-link\">Register of Directors’ interests - available on request</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"mailto:gdfenquiries@nda.gov.uk\" class=\"govuk-link\">RWM Information Asset Register - available on request</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"the-services-we-offer\">The services we offer</h3>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>You can <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/our-work-with-radioactive-waste-producers\" class=\"govuk-link\">find out about our work with radioactive waste producers</a>\n</li>\n  <li>Our <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/announcements?departments%5B%5D=radioactive-waste-management\" class=\"govuk-link\">recent announcements</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"fees\">Fees</h3>\n<p>NWS does not charge for the provision of information listed in the scheme. NWS retains the right to charge for the written requests in line with the SI2004/3244 The Freedom of Information and Data Protection (Appropriate Limit and Fees) Regulations 2004.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"written-requests\">Written Requests</h3>\n<p>Information held by a public authority that is not published under this scheme can be requested in writing.\nIts provision will be considered in accordance with the provisions of the Freedom of Information Act. Please contact the NWS Freedom of Information Manager using the following contact details:</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact contact\" id=\"contact_4112\">\n    <p class=\"govuk-body\">Freedom of Information</p>\n\n\n    <div>\n        <p class=\"govuk-body govuk-!-margin-bottom-4\">\n          Email <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"mailto:FOIrequest@nuclearwasteservices.uk\">FOIrequest@nuclearwasteservices.uk</a>\n        </p>\n\n\n    </div>\n\n    <p class=\"govuk-body\">Nuclear Waste Services Limited (NWS Ltd) is a subsidiary of the Nuclear Decommissioning Authority (NDA).</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>" .
